{
  "texts": [
    "Subsequently, they have joined many seminars to sharpen their expertise in the field, so they can grade exam papers fairly.",
    "In this regard, items in the exam were refined by the whole team in order not to make any grave mistakes.",
    "Besides, research instruments were tested by other students who had the same characteristics.",
    "Based on their responses, some papers were evaluated in the meetings to dispel doubts and increase the confidence of raters.",
    "Moreover, researchers requested to grade papers blindly by three raters."
  ]
}